title: The Killing of Shireen Abu Aqleh
itunes:title: The Killing of Shireen Abu Aqleh
description:
Shereen continues the conversation about Palestine by discussing the murder of Palestinian-American journalist Shireen Abu Aqleh and the violence perpetrated by Israeli police during her funeral.
